::Striker::

Striker walks through the forest. He was almost to the position of the two bots.

He takes a deep breath. This was insane, going to a predacon and a possibly hostile neutral bot. He sighs. It was either that or death by loss of mech fluid.

He walks on, the cave that the energy signatures were coming from now in view.
